---
title: Roast Pumpkin & Parsnip Freekeh Salad with Honey Dressing, Mint Yoghurt & Feta
description: Let’s get freekeh (pronounced free-kuh)! Sorry. We had to. Freekeh is an ancient grain and nutrition powerhouse often mentioned alongside superfood heroes like quinoa and farro. With its roasted nuttiness, it's our new favourite base for a nourishing bowl of big flavours. You’re gonna love it.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roast-pumpkin-parsnip-freekeh-salad-9b4564df.jpg
